&lt;p&gt;There were still a few things I&#39;ve been doing more with Still&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://anchor.fm/sia-sarvaiya&#34;&gt;the phobias podcast&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/anchor-generated-image-bank/production/podcast_uploaded_nologo400/9576437/9576437-1603090521699-2ca8fedcc2d0a.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;phobias podcast&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I am always looking for new podcasts to get into. Sia is creating a podcast that looks at a number of phobias (one per episode).&lt;/p&gt;

